It simply joins properties with "and", resulting in clunky sentences.  I'll focus on improving sentence structure by introducing more contextual phrasing and attempting to create more natural flow, particularly for relationships between people (discoverer, almaMater, etc.).

```diff

        sentence += " " + " and ".join(properties)
        combined_sentences.append(sentence)
>>>>>>> REPLACE
        sentence += ", " + ", ".join(properties) + "."
        combined_sentences.append(sentence)
```
Please fix it to the correct format.
